Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw arrived back to the warmer climates of Africa, flying in 
robot mode. She landed and transformed to beast mode. She looked 
around. She had strange thoughts that the encounter with the Vok was 
a dream. It reoccured in her conscious mind for some moments. 

She shook her head. Maybe it was her head playing games on her.
